(ROOT
  (S
    (NP (NNP Tom))
    (VP (VBD had)
      (S
        (VP (TO to)
          (VP (VB fix)
            (NP
              (NP (DT some) (NNS things))
              (FRAG
                (SBAR
                  (X
                    (ADVP (RB around))
                    (NP (DT the) (NN house))
                    (. .))
                  (S
                    (NP (PRP He))
                    (VP (VBD had)
                      (S
                        (VP (TO to)
                          (VP (VB fix)
                            (NP (DT the) (NN door))))))))
                (. .)))
            (SBAR
              (S
                (S
                  (NP (PRP He))
                  (VP (VBD had)
                    (S
                      (VP (TO to)
                        (VP (VB fix)
                          (NP (DT the) (NN window))))))
                  (. .))
                (CC But)
                (S
                  (SBAR (IN before)
                    (S
                      (NP (PRP he))
                      (VP (VBD did)
                        (NP (NN anything))
                        (S
                          (S
                            (NP (PRP he))
                            (VP (VBD had)
                              (S
                                (VP (TO to)
                                  (VP (VB fix)
                                    (NP (DT the) (NN toilet))))))
                            (. .))
                          (S
                            (NP (NNP Tom))
                            (VP (VBD called)
                              (PRT (RP over))
                              (NP
                                (NP (PRP$ his) (JJS best) (NN friend))
                                (FRAG
                                  (NP
                                    (NP (NNP Jim))
                                    (SBAR
                                      (S
                                        (VP (TO to)
                                          (VP (VB help)
                                            (NP (PRP him))))))
                                    (. .))
                                  (: Jim)
                                  (VP (VBD brought)
                                    (PP (IN with)
                                      (NP (PRP him)))
                                    (NP
                                      (NP (PRP$ his) (NNS friends))
                                      (NP (NNP Molly)
                                        (CC and)
                                        (NNP Holly))))
                                  (. .)))))
                          (S
                            (NP (NNP Tom))
                            (VP (VBD thought)
                              (SBAR (IN that)
                                (S
                                  (NP (NNP Jim))
                                  (VP (VBD was)
                                    (VP (VBG going)
                                      (S
                                        (VP (TO to)
                                          (VP (VB bring)
                                            (NP
                                              (NP (NNP Dolly))
                                              (PP (IN with)
                                                (NP (PRP him)))))))))))))
                          (CC but)
                          (S
                            (NP (PRP he))
                            (VP (VBD did) (RB n't))
                            (. .))
                          (S
                            (NP
                              (NP (DT The) (CD four))
                              (PP (IN of)
                                (NP (PRP them))))
                            (VP (VBD got)
                              (S
                                (VP (TO to)
                                  (VP (VB work)
                                    (SBAR
                                      (SINV
                                        (ADVP (RB right) (RB away) (. .))
                                        (VP (VBG Fixing)
                                          (NP
                                            (NP (DT the) (NN toilet))
                                            (SBAR
                                              (S
                                                (VP (VBD was)
                                                  (NP
                                                    (NP (NNP easy) (. .))
                                                    (VP (VBG Fixing)
                                                      (NP
                                                        (NP (DT the) (NN door))
                                                        (SBAR
                                                          (S
                                                            (VP (VBD was)
                                                              (ADVP (RB also))
                                                              (ADJP (JJ easy))))))
                                                      (FRAG (CC but)
                                                        (NP
                                                          (NP (NNP fixing))
                                                          (SBAR
                                                            (S
                                                              (NP (DT the) (NN window))
                                                              (VP (VBD was)
                                                                (ADJP (RB very) (JJ hard)))))
                                                          (. .))
                                                        (SBAR
                                                          (S
                                                            (NP (DT The) (NN window))
                                                            (VP
                                                              (VP (VBD was)
                                                                (VP (VBN stuck)))
                                                              (CC and)
                                                              (VP (MD could) (RB not)
                                                                (VP (VB be)
                                                                  (VP (VBN opened)))))))
                                                        (. .)))
                                                    (SBAR
                                                      (S
                                                        (NP (PRP They))
                                                        (VP (RB all) (VBN pushed)
                                                          (PP (IN on)
                                                            (NP (DT the) (NN window)))))))))))
                                          (FRAG
                                            (ADJP (RB really) (JJ hard))
                                            (SBAR (IN until)
                                              (S
                                                (ADVP (RB finally))
                                                (NP (PRP it))
                                                (VP (VBD opened))))
                                            (. .)))
                                        (VP
                                          (ADVP (RB Once)
                                            (NP (DT the) (NN window)))
                                          (VBD was)
                                          (VP (VBN fixed)))
                                        (NP
                                          (NP (DT the) (CD four))
                                          (PP (IN of)
                                            (NP (PRP them)))
                                          (VP
                                            (VP (VBN made)
                                              (NP (DT a)
                                                (ADJP (JJ delicious))
                                                (NN dinner)))
                                            (CC and)
                                            (VP (VBN talked)
                                              (PP (IN about)
                                                (NP
                                                  (NP (DT all))
                                                  (PP (IN of)
                                                    (NP (DT the) (JJ good) (NN work)))))
                                              (SBAR (IN that)
                                                (S
                                                  (NP (PRP they))
                                                  (VP (VBD had)
                                                    (VP (VBN done))))))))
                                        (. .))))))))))))
                  (NP (NNP Tom))
                  (VP (VBD was)
                    (ADJP (JJ glad))))))
            (SBAR (IN that)
              (S
                (NP (PRP he))
                (VP (VBD had)
                  (NP (JJ such) (JJ good) (NNS friends))))))))
      (S
        (VP (TO to)
          (VP (VB help)
            (NP (PRP him))
            (PP (IN with)
              (NP (PRP$ his) (NN work)))))))
    (. .)))

                                      (NP (EX There))

                                          (NP (NNP Thomas))))))))

                                              (VP (VBD barked))))

                  (NP (PRP It))

                      (NP (DT a) (JJ new) (JJ red) (NN collar))
                      (PP (IN with)
                        (NP
                          (NP (DT a) (JJ shiny) (NN name) (NN tag))
                          (PP (IN on)
                            (NP (PRP it)))))))
                  (. .))

    (NP (NNP Anne))
    (VP (VBZ is)
      (NP
        (NP (NNP hungry) (. .))
        (SBAR
          (S
            (NP (PRP She))
            (VP (VBZ wants)
              (S
                (VP (TO to)
                  (VP (VB eat)
                    (S
                      (S
                        (ADVP (RB somewhere)
                          (PP (IN in)
                            (FRAG
                              (NP
                                (NP (NNP town) (. .))
                                (SBAR
                                  (S
                                    (NP (EX There))
                                    (VP (VBZ is)
                                      (NP
                                        (NP (DT a) (JJ popular) (NN diner))
                                        (PP (IN in)
                                          (NP (NN town)))))))
                                (. .)))))
                        (NP (PRP She))
                        (VP
                          (VP (VBZ goes)
                            (ADVP (RB there)))
                          (CC and)
                          (VP (VBZ asks)

                            (SBAR (IN if)
                              (S
                                (NP (PRP she))
                                (VP (MD can)
                                  (VP (VB get)
                                    (NP
                                      (NP (NNS fries))
                                      (CC and)
                                      (NP (DT a) (NN chocolate) (NN milkshake))))))
                              (. .)))))
                      (S
                        (NP (PRP$ Her) (NNS friends))
                        (VP (VBP come)
                          (PP (IN into)
                            (NP
                              (NP
                                (NP (DT the))
                                (NP (NN diner)))
                              (CC and)
                              (NP
                                (VP (VB sit))
                                (PP (IN with)
                                  (NP (PRP her))))
                              (. .)
                              (NP
                                (NP (PRP$ Their) (NNS names))

                                  (S
                                    (VP (VBP are)
                                      (NP (NNP Jane) (, ,) (NNP Jake)
                                        (CC and)
                                        (NNP Dave))))))
                              (. .)
                              (NP
                                (NP (DT All))
                                (PP (IN of)
                                  (SBAR
                                    (S
                                      (NP (PRP them))
                                      (VP (VBP are)
                                        (ADJP
                                          (NP (CD 15) (NNS years))
                                          (JJ old)))))))
                              (. .)
                              (NP
                                (NP (NNP Jake))
                                (VP (VBZ gets)
                                  (NP (DT a) (JJ big) (NN cheeseburger))
                                  (PP (IN with)
                                    (NP (NNS onions)))))
                              (. .)
                              (NP
                                (NP (NNP Jane))
                                (VP (VBZ wants)
                                  (NP (DT a) (NN vanilla) (NN ice) (NN cream) (NN cone))
                                  (PP (IN with)
                                    (NP (NNP sprinkles)))))

                                (NP (NNP Dave))
                                (SBAR
                                  (S
                                    (VP (VBZ does) (RB n't)
                                      (VP (VB eat)
                                        (NP (NN anything)))))))
                              (. .)
                              (NP
                                (NP (PRP He) (NNS talks))
                                (PP (IN with)
                                  (NP (PRP them)))
                                (SBAR
                                  (S
                                    (SBAR
                                      (ADVP (RB instead) (. .))
                                      (IN After)
                                      (S
                                        (NP (PRP they))
                                        (VP (VBP finish)
                                          (S
                                            (VP (VBG eating))))))
                                    (, ,)
                                    (NP (PRP they))
                                    (VP (VBP go)
                                      (ADVP (RB back))
                                      (PP (TO to)
                                        (NP
                                          (NP (NNP Jane) (POS 's))
                                          (NN house)
                                          (S
                                            (VP (TO to)
                                              (VP
                                                (VP (VB hang)
                                                  (PRT (RP out)))
                                                (CC and)
                                                (VP (VB play)
                                                  (NP (NNS games))))))))))))
                              (. .)
                              (NP
                                (NP (NNP Dave))

                                  (S

                                        (NP (JJS most))
                                        (PP (IN of)
                                          (NP (DT the) (NN puzzle) (NNS games))))))))
                              (. .)

                                (NP (NNP Jane))
                                (VP (VBZ beats)
                                  (NP (PRP them))
                                  (PP (IN at)
                                    (NP (DT a) (JJ few)))))
                              (. .)
                              (NP
                                (NP (PRP They))
                                (SBAR
                                  (S
                                    (VP (VBP 're)
                                      (VP (VBG racing)
                                        (NP (NNS games)))))))
                              (. .)
                              (NP
                                (NP (NNP Dave))
                                (SBAR
                                  (S
                                    (VP (VBZ leaves)
                                      (PP (IN after))))))
                              (, an)
                              (NP
                                (NP (NNP hour) (. .))
                                (SBAR
                                  (S
                                    (NP (PRP He))
                                    (VP (VBZ needs)
                                      (S
                                        (VP (TO to)
                                          (VP (VB go)
                                            (PRT (RP do))
                                            (NP (PRP$ his) (NN reading) (NN homework))))))))))))
                        (. .))
                      (S
                        (NP (NNP Jake)
                          (CC and)
                          (NNP Anne))
                        (VP (VBP leave)
                          (NP (DT that) (NN evening))
                          (SBAR (IN because)
                            (S
                              (NP (PRP it))
                              (VP (VBZ 's)
                                (NP (DT a) (NN school) (NN night))))))
                        (. .))
                      (S
                        (NP (PRP They))
